spec_data.Name: texlive-lualibs
spec_data.Description:
Lualibs is a collection of Lua modules useful for general
programming. The bundle is based on lua modules shipped with
ConTeXt, and are made available in this bundle for use
independent of ConTeXt.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:37:42 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Additional Lua functions for LuaTeX macro programmers
